# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Romanian translation — HELD BACK FROM PUBLICATION
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Romanian (`ro`) edition lives in the working tree so it can be written and
# reviewed locally, but it is intentionally EXCLUDED from version control until
# it is approved for public release.
#
# TO UNBLOCK (publish the Romanian edition):
#   1. Delete or comment out the single line `docs/ro/` below.
#   2. git add docs/ro && git commit -m "docs: publish Romanian (ro) edition"
#   3. git push
#
# Until then, `docs/ro/` is untracked and will never be pushed.
docs/ro/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rendered diagram artifacts (Mermaid sources in diagrams/*.mmd ARE tracked;
# locally-rendered images are not — GitHub renders the Mermaid blocks directly)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
diagrams/*.svg
diagrams/*.png

